svg.source: Title: System Auto Assign Gift Exchange Guests User-->User Interface: Click Assign Exchange Guests button User Interface-->User: Display Assign Exchange Guests Page User-->User Interface: Select system auto assignment User Interface-->User Interface: Validates Data Note right of User Interface: If error, display message User Interface-->User Interface: Confirms this will override previous assignments User Interface-->Server API: Calls auto assign guests API Server API-->Server API: Validates Data Note right of Server API: If error, return with error Note ritgt of Server API: repeat for each guest Server API-->Database: Assign gifting guest to guest Database-->Server API: Saved guest Server API-->Email Platform: Send email to gifting guest with assignment details Server API-->User Interface: Success result User Interface-->User Interface: Show success message
